snippet.textDisplay:
@SupraDarky ...And/Or a Soul II Soul album-This sounds very similar to their song 'Keep On Movin,' as well as Eric B. & Rakim's 'Paid In Full,' both of which were released prior to this game.

Anyway, I have so many fond memories of both this track and the soundtrack as a whole.  I remember pausing the game quite often (Especially on the stages this track was featured on), turning the volume all the way up on my floor-model T.V., and jamming lol  SAI was definitely some of Koshiro's best work...
snippet.textOriginal:
